latestIgtvVideos.caption:
So today, I would like to dedicate something to my mother. 
I hope, it touches your heart; the way you have touched; my heart.
Mom, you mean the world to me.
Today what ever I am, is because of you.
I respect you even more, after becoming a mother myself.
I hope, I would be able to do at least half of what you have done for me and Vreyaan.
Its you; who have made me believe; the hand that rocks the cradle; rules the world…
This one’s for you, mom 

I would also like to thank @marathonbuoy @nimaaya_health @gr8weekender for organising this beautiful event 
A special thanks to @theministryofmemories @kalyugkakabir @pujarahulkedia for this beautifully captured video 
Also my co dancers without whom this was not possible @prachi.bhanawala @dance.bhavisha_kalra @juhi.smiles 

Thank you @raveenasahnii for all your help and choreographing it in just 2 days 

The glam look is created by @rahulssalon 
Outfit courtesy @qudo.mn
